ine;">FDA Completes First Pre-Market Consultation for Human Food Made Using=
 Animal Cell Culture Technology</a></strong></p><p style=3D"color: #404040;=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><em>From the FDA<=
/em></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #51b4e9; margin: 20px 0=
; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>The U.S. Food and Drug Admi=
