 and at scale, the ability to predictably grow supply to meet growing deman=
d for meat. In comparison to plant-based meats, cultivated meats should mai=
ntain a more natural nutritional profile, authentic taste and texture profi=
le, and potentially be more sustainable at scale.</p><p style=3D"color: #40=
4040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Over 70 bill=
ion &#8212; a number too big to wrap your head around &#8212; chickens are =
slaughtered each year. Who knows how far off we are from replacing even jus=
